Readiness' angle of the brief.
    + The 'Agentic Workflows' example regarding IT license auditing is concrete, relatable for procurement officers, and
demonstrates high actionability.
    + Strong SEO alignment through the use of high-intent technical terms like SOC2 Type II, data residency, and the 
'SSO Tax'.
